			<div class="commentcount">238</div>

				<p>I have made these twice now and they are delicious.  The second time I ran out of white flour and had to use a cup of whole wheat flour.  They were a bit drier but still delicious.  I also tried flash freezing as suggested for the first time.  This is a wonderful site!</p>
	</li>
		
		
		
	
	</ul>

 

